  "body": "<div id=\"post-view221164052968\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea221164052968\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">음식 사진 좀 다시 올려볼까해요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">ㅋㅋ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이번주는 이수한의원에 필요한 물품들을 사려다니고 있어요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">몇가지 필요한 물품들을 사고 식사하러갔습니다</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">상도동에있는 올바른식당이라는곳인데</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f76b0b3d78de7a59.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTc2/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzQ5OTIy.vPBudxjzEPnd5tU2KtGyL5j5dk-Fl6wtpsYSPk60sTAg.l9bIrsKsHWPAQRDQ24k490G2Pn9KMFe9hODa9xFG_u0g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190921918.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f76b0b3d78de7a59.jpg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">원장님은 김치찌개</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">저와 정샘은 뚝불고기를 시켰어요</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6fd3d5ff3a4f506a.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfOTUg/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUwMzgz.KUfka9tzf2pG6KWnRZEPIN_DY6s7VwtVXgKvL1BdG7Mg.yu9gysABghkwzj3cSmGqs5tgPXiulxglYlTicwCaHDsg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190922996.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6fd3d5ff3a4f506a.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bca7c8492941874c.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMjUw/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUwNTUx.lv4FUR2F0jFZHBSoRlQ7sviI5kMid9bgmeEZzGMl9tIg.Z5iAss3fJ2t6CbV95QBDfxD_iSbeHEELlz4DsfiZ7-Mg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190923522.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bca7c8492941874c.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">불고기 짱맛있어요~</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">_____________________________________________________</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">이수한의원 식구들이&nbsp;</span></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">우리 이수한의원에 내원하는 환자분이 운영하시는</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">식당에 다녀왔어요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">남성역 근처에있는 아주 작고 아늑한 식당인데</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cfdb8abb8b69aac5.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTQy/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUwNzQx.iY020XyLgI2AvJgZEOAHsLqvmiiYfaZqDdJVux1CmEgg.h0XFl8ad4Gex2xIAVCaBuvlr6hYo-xwd6E73AxEc2dog.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190907395.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cfdb8abb8b69aac5.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/32eb4be79018e1af.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMjcy/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUwOTE5.33qpONZgkd4rJOlgKAR6EQMLasm2EMZyfzvs-4-IyLQg.Hsk8QcsVnoCwa9CjLVnP9SaBl7duTZ_TXDXVkIq0NLIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190906100.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/32eb4be79018e1af.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d73480e0500e8f24.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTQz/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUxMDQz.kmZqo5m31DwmOYLXRFgRpa8ZWvlYJdA65GHM9P3-wScg.6C-GJFkWXg7E9iazpLyIMHQMm0ySDeRjU7qlUdXOu8sg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190906549.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d73480e0500e8f24.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">여기도 너무 맛있네요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">다음에 또 가야겠어요~</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">_____________________________________________________</p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">퇴근하고 여자들끼리 치킨먹으로&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">치킨집으로 고고~</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5c6a777e6ff0a09b.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTIg/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUxNDM3.yFGA6Q7JsvkZLwvrSOS0PVVOag5UGC7kSACgHEqSBVYg.G2nC-ewZ6uBZI5yInvtkFLo3oxps4vxHiitXBZz--m0g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190918804.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5c6a777e6ff0a09b.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/91c8d15e8ab4f948.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTQ4/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUxNjE2.qWb3oEUlm5SSH2huLX0OhkF8qzEtrQe76WjX1R9xqm8g.iSBemoionrEfqNsTORrjRvUuU3NB454KxFQRqltX5Zgg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190919505.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/91c8d15e8ab4f948.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">반반 시키고</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이런얘기 저런얘기 하다가</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">골뱅이소면 하나 추가!</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d3edc2cb7166bc74.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMTA1/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUxODEy.9xDJRqWEbB5gsL8jSqy599AYjbCbJbhkw_QQzrnmppog.eiFGki44Mxa5m2Dc4fQvlPP4hmrJ01z5wwTnKGXzd2kg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190917969.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d3edc2cb7166bc74.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/10b520eca81e4308.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMjkw/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUxOTgy.5toL_49Hz3pyB4R8-uS6XPLzaUdcw00HhMoGU6k6gRQg.BNas7tnspPNaxALTv1E7vCqp7MLgyckwODfcpu8WEDMg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190917341.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/10b520eca81e4308.jpg\"></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">우리동내에 이렇게 맛있게 하는 치킨집이있는지 몰랐네요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">앞으로 치킨은 여기서 질릴때까지 먹는걸로....</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">_____________________________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">오늘 점심은 순두부찌개</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/977cfa3ee3a1f17a.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfNTMg/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUxMjU2.fMonIB6ddnOG0V88fIa288_OWWNl7b8EZHyck7zAKwIg.nQPVycj_8yunFP6Lg6NHG-G3zNy9lJrKjOpDumkjfqEg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190901753.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/977cfa3ee3a1f17a.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/feae7940a2149ad2.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMjIg/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUyMjEw.KxH5tY1SyEiNfcM8xVTuaWLMTSquTZsz0xATgIlCbDgg.OLODHXznu6x3LyIkXGpAq5LbI1t4H-1Van_8MayWwVog.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190901303.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/feae7940a2149ad2.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a20b633e16749a5b.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:400px; rheight:400px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTVfMjU3/MDAxNTEzMzM4NzUyNDky.RC8mAmJoFrPanFOFOCCSy8I1TGUQCHRQ3JDxteFNMg4g.TPEbzELJS5uA9t8HIyYxmVupe7pXHCz56BRmeuudV1Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171215_190900771.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E67A1E8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a20b633e16749a5b.jpg\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</span></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이수한의원 뒷골목에있는 보리밥집인데</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">저번에 보리밥 먹은적이&nbsp;있어서</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">오늘은 순두부를 시켜보았는데 순두부도 맛있어요</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">근데 제가 글쓰면서 느낀건데</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">저는 안맛있는 음식이없네요 ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">사실 다 맛있어요 저는...</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이렇게 돼지가 되어가고있는 제모습은 안비밀</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e99805d963476e94.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-12\"></a>&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
